"{\"uid\": \"toronto.citynews.ca-2024-06-27-dutch-beach-volleyball-player-who-served-time-for-rape-has-qualified-for-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Adjust preferences  With your consent we may collect cookies and information to enhance our service, and improve your experience.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These cookies and data are essential for browsing our website and allowing services.\", \"from\": 131, \"to\": 215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Examples include, session, authentication, and security cookies.\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These cookies and data enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and personalized content.\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These cookies and data inform us which pages are most informative and engaging via analytics.\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 478, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These cookies may track data across websites for marketing and interest-based advertising to provide personalized content, offers, and advertisements.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Toronto  By The Associated Press  Posted June 27, 2024 1:12 pm.\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 632, \"end\": 639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.785809484073448e-15, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last Updated June 27, 2024 5:26 pm.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"THE HAGUE, Netherlands (AP) - A Dutch beach volleyball player convicted and imprisoned eight years ago for raping an underage girl in Britain has qualified for the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 734, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hague\", \"score\": 0.9999350376421074, \"rank\": 6.395292659654769e-05, \"text\": \"THE HAGUE\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hague\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hague\"}, {\"begin\": 745, \"end\": 756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999929915511558, \"rank\": 6.945291593158148e-06, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999994861355, \"rank\": 5.1366878503801e-10, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 766, \"end\": 771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.8071188673874806, \"rank\": 0.23164945982824395, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 868, \"end\": 875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999999938734165, \"rank\": 6.024443716676745e-08, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Steven van de Veldeand partner Matthew Immers were one of two men's teams from the Netherlands that qualified for the beach volleyball competition at the Paris Games, which open on July 26 in the French capital.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 998, \"end\": 1009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999929915511558, \"rank\": 6.945291593158148e-06, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 1111, \"end\": 1117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9990082998334777, \"rank\": 0.0008657801553856922, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most beach pairs qualify for the 24-team Olympic field by earning points on the international tour; Van de Velde and Immers were 11th on the points list.\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I understand that in the run-up to the biggest sporting event in the world, this can attract the attention of international media,\\\" Van de Velde said in a statement posted on the website of the Netherlands Volleyball Federation.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999929915511558, \"rank\": 6.945291593158148e-06, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volleyball\", \"score\": 0.9999976621525136, \"rank\": 2.2155926600483657e-06, \"text\": \"Volleyball\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volleyball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volleyball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I cannot reverse it, so I will have to bear the consequences.\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been the biggest mistake of my life.\\\"\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde was sentenced to four years in prison in Britain after being convicted in 2016 of having sex with an underage girl he reportedly got to know online.\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1675, \"end\": 1682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999999938734165, \"rank\": 6.024443716676745e-08, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was transferred to the Netherlands under a treaty between the countries, and resentenced according to Dutch law.\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1809, \"end\": 1820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999929915511558, \"rank\": 6.945291593158148e-06, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 1888, \"end\": 1893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.8071188673874806, \"rank\": 0.23164945982824395, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After his release, Van de Velde sought and received professional counseling.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has demonstrated to those around him - privately and professionally - self-insight and reflection,\\\" the federation said.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It added that both the federation and the Netherlands Olympic Committee \\\"rely on the opinions of experts who consider the chance of recidivism nil.\\\"\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2145, \"end\": 2174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Netherlands Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutch Olympic committee said Van de Velde, now 29, met the conditions required to return after a conviction and resumed his career in 2017 \\\"after an intensive professionally supervised process.\\\"\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2257, \"end\": 2280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9946011395003685e-24, \"text\": \"Dutch Olympic committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Van de Velde now meets all the qualification requirements for the Olympic Games and is therefore part of the team,\\\" the committee said.\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The international volleyball federation said it \\\"recognizes that this is a highly sensitive matter\\\" but said team selection is the responsibility of the national Olympic committee \\\"while respecting the eligibility criteria.\\\"\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"___  AP Summer Olympics:https://apnews.com/hub/2024-paris-olympic-games    The Associated Press    Police say a suspect is in custody after a man was critically injured in a stabbing in midtown Toronto.\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 3019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3011, \"end\": 3018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.785809484073448e-15, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Investigators were called to Yonge Street and Berwick Avenue, south of Eglinton Avenue, just after...  8h ago  They are easy-to-use devices that anyone can operate, and they\\u00a0have been pro